reviewText: dvd's arrived in a very reasonable and were very well packaged. I and a huge vampire movie fan and always try to get all vampire movies available .  5 stars
Always loved this movie so happy was able to find it on DVD.  I already owned it on VHS but was more than happy to buy it on DVD as well, thats how much I love this movie hehe.

I have been looking for this movie for a vary long time. I found it for a realy good price compares to the outhers that wanted a arm and a leg for it. This item arived intime for christmas when i ordered it.
This isn't the worst vampire movie but it is dated. This movie does have the vampire levitated and impaled at the end.

Originally saw this in the 80's because I had a friend who worked on the film.  It seemed pretty good at the time, but rewatching 20 years later, not so much.  Also the dvd I got was REALLLY bad, the sound was terrible.
